A chunga kan hmuhte khi a lo chhuahna chu mihring thinlung, rul thlah aṭangin a ni a, Krista aṭanga chhuak pakhat mah a awm lo. Khing sual rah chi hrang hrangte khi, khawvelin an chhia leh ṭha hriatna danin an do va. Pathian fate erawh chuan a lo chhuahna thinlung, mihring chhia leh ṭha hriatnain a hmuh phak hauh loh chu, Chhandamtun Kalvari thing anchhedawng kraws-a khaikan 'ruang' ngei, thlana a chhilh hnan tawh daih kha a ni tih an hre chhuak ṭhin. A tir ata bumtu khan, a ngai tein chu ruang chu bumna hmang bawkin a rawn phawrh leh ṭhin a ni reng si a (Rom 6:6). Chu sual bawih ata chu Krista'n min chhuah tawh a, chu thutak chu kan luah zel theih nan, a tuamtu râng pan te hi hal ral a ngai fo ṭhin reng a ni (Lev. 4:10). Vanah chuan Krista taksa chauh a cheng thei a, Krista taksa ni lo, i hriat nangmah kha telh ve i tum apiangin Eden huan pawnah i awm hlauh ṭhin. Lalber a lo kal leh niah pawh, Adama thisen hi a rawn ko tel dawn lo va, ama thisen ngei chu a rawn lam leh dawn a ni.
Krista thisenah i ei ve ngai tawh em le? Thlarau Thianghlim ngei chuan Krista engah, amah Krista aṭanga chhuak felna leh mahni aṭanga chhuak felna ngei chu thliar hran theihna min pe zel se, kan sualna chauh ni mai lo, kan felna ngei chu khenbehin Kristaah lo awm rawh se. A thawktu chu Thlarau Thianghlim a ni a, a hmanrua chu Krista kraws a ni a, a din chhuah chu kohhran thianghlim chu a ni. Thlarau a nih pawhin Thlarau Thianghlim chauh, hmangaihna a nih pawhin hmangaihna thianghlim chauh, indona a nih pawhin indona thianghlim chauh chu Krista aṭanga chhuak chu a ni. Thianghlimna lo chuan tuman Lalpa hmel an hmu lo vang. Krista aṭanga felna lo chhuak ni lo, felna leh dikna kan chapopui ngei hi, phairuam indo zawha Setana hmanrua lo lang ṭhin chu a ni (1 Lalte 28:31-43).
He phaizawl indonaah hian, hnehtu chuan min hneh zawh vek kan phal zan lohna hian tlang indona a hring chhuak ṭhin a ni. Indona thianghlim reng rengah chuan a kaptu leh a dawngtu kan awm ṭhin a. A dawngtuah i ṭanin a kaptu thinlunga Krista hmangaihna mei kang hi i hriat thiam theih nan leh mihring en lova, Lalpa chauh chu i thinlunga i hmuh theih nan, a kaptu thinlung hi han ennawn leh rawh le.
Indona thianghlim tak takah chuan, Lalpaa innghah mai pawh a ni lo, amah Lalpa ngei hmangaih let ngawih ngawihna a lo thleng a. Thinlung hian sual te tak te pawh a do chak zek zek a, indonaa Pathian ngei chu thinlungah hian a vir vet vet reng a. Chumi rual chuan, mahni ngei pawh ral zelnain a thawk a. Mahni inbih dek dukna te a ral vek a, inbih hman lo lekin Lalpa leh a kohhran hmangaih ngawih ngawihnaah chuan, Chhandamtu thisen luanna Kalvari ngei mai chu, a tlang chawpin thinlungah a rawn inhung lut a; chu tlangah chuan hlinglukhum leh a tawrhna kraws, lungngaihna leh thlamuanna inkawp, sual huat ngawih ngawihna leh Krista hmangaihna a lo alh chhuak a, thinlung hian, "keimah ka ni lo, Krista zawk a ni" a ti mawlh mawlh reng a. Hetia indona Pathian, Krista rilru keini mi te ber thinlunga a chen ve chuan, Lalpa hmangaihtute lo hlutzia kha, thinlung hian mittui nen a chhiar chhuak ve zu nia. Chu hmunah ngei chuan kal hmasate thawm kan han hre ve ta a, kan hmaa mi huai kalte lo din nghehna hmun leh, an hnehna puanzar lo phe vet vet ṭhin te chuan, Krista zara hnehtu zingah kan lo tel ve reng ta mai tih min hriattir a lo ni reng a. Chu nun mak tak mai chu, "Amen, Lal Isua ta a ni."
Mahni ngei pawh mi sual nih inhre reng si a, sual huatnaa kan khat tlat hi, 'Krista zawk' a lo ni e. Mahni inring nung chawp lova, rinnaa kal mai zawk a, mi chak lo ber pawhin, "Min tichaktuah chuan engkim ka ti thei a ni," tia hnehna thawm ri chuan thim lal kulh chu a ṭhiat lo thei lo a ni (Heb. 11:2-40).

Ka Chhandamtu, ka fak a che, Nangma ta chauh ka ni a; Thisena min sil fai vangin, Beram No ropui rawh se.

